{"lemma":"عَدْوَى","slug":"عَدْوَى","root":"ع.د.#","root_slug":"ع-د-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-د-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28384"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"infection, contagion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hostile action"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From ع د و (ʕ d w); compare عَدَا (ʕadā, “to infect”).\n\nFrom ع د و (ʕ d w); compare عَدَا (ʕadā, “to engage in hostile action”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28384","headword_ar":"عَدْوَى","root":"Edw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other disease, that passes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is transitive, from one to another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a transitive disease;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and such is said to be the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jarab","text_ar":"جَرَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baraS","text_ar":"بَرَص"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramad","text_ar":"رَمَد"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSobap","text_ar":"حَصْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ju*aAm","text_ar":"جُذَام"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabaA='","text_ar":"وَبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"judariY~","text_ar":"جُدَرِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Kull p. 259.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuqar~ibohu minohu","text_ar":"لَا تُقَرِّبْهُ مِنْهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA_in~a bihi EadowaY","text_ar":"فَاـِنَّ بِهِ عَدْوَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou bring him near to him, for in him is a disease such as the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab, that is transitive from one to another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"transition of the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other disease, from him that has it to another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA, TK:) the subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEoduw","text_ar":"يَعْدُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of the mange, or scab, expl. above, as meaning “ it passes ” &c. (Msb. [See 1, first quarter.]) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA EadowaY","text_ar":"لَا عَدْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA yuEodiY $aYo'N","text_ar":"لَا يُعْدِى شَىْءٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayoy^FA","text_ar":"شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(meaning disease)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"does not pass"},{"kind":"text","text":"by its own agency"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S;) or [lit.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there is no transition of the mange,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scab,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other disease, from him that has it to another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaAdN","text_ar":"فَسَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Badness, corruptness, unsoundness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (K, TA. [In the CK erroneously written in this sense"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eudow`Y","text_ar":"عُدْوٰى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which, however, being an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaA","text_ar":"عَدَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadaA","text_ar":"عَدَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v., may be correctly used as having the same, or nearly the same, meaning.]) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi EadowaY","text_ar":"بِهِ عَدْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, is badness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TK.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A demand that one makes upon a prefect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"governor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"judge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to aid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assist, him against him who has wronged him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to inflict penal retribution on him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for his wrongdoing to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, Msb.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Aid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assistance, against a wrongdoer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"required of a judge, for the bringing into his presence the antagonist:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a signet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of clay, given by the judge as a token to denote the summoning of him whose presence is required."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","TK","IF","Msb","Mgh"]}]}}